subtitleNullable: Predict and Visualize Traffic in Salt Lake City, Utah
descriptionNullable:
Hourly traffic data for 50 locations near Salt Lake City Utah during January 2022. I created this dataset to analyze the temporal and spatial correlations in traffic. 

Data was sourced at: https://www.udot.utah.gov/connect/business/traffic-data/traffic-statistics/

Longitude and Latitude coordinates for each point are found in the meta-data file.
